methods.shouldLog:
Should this item be logged?

:param duration: (long) - the duration (or usage) of the item
:param repeatedReads: (long) - the number of repeated reads which occurred
:param initialReads: (long) - the number of initial reads which occurred
:return: (boolean) true if the item exceeds our logging threshold, and thus should be logged

text:
This class encapsulates the parameters that control whether a given item (nugget or entry interval) is logged to
 one of our three performance logs.
